Frequently asked questions
Form scoring is a simpler and faster way based on our expertise and your internal company experience, it sets up quickly but is not always precise because there is always a human factor.
ML scoring is based on big data analysis and it maximizes the quality of the prediction, but it takes more time to set up.
Within a week, you can leverage our expertise and your audience knowledge to start scoring and routing leads effectively.
ML scoring is available with sufficient traffic accumulation, and it depends on the sales volumes.
Our solution integrates seamlessly with popular CRMs like HubSpot and Salesforce. This allows you to leverage AI insights directly within your existing sales workflows. But it also offers custom solutions for a truly tailored experience for your sales pipeline optimization.
NextBuyer takes care of all the technical setup, including CRM, form and ML integration.  Just communicate your needs, and we'll get you up and running quickly.
Our data collection process is similar to familiar tools like Google Analytics. We prioritize user privacy and security, and can always assist you with GDPR compliance if needed.
